data.description: This beautiful home in Buford is amazing. It offers you a 7 room home; 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, including a bedroom and full bath on the main floor. This is a DR Horton "Smart Home", with many upgrades - pre-engineered floors, private fenced in back yard, and active swim/tennis community. Located in top rated Buford school system in Seckinger High School district. This is very convenient to Lake Lanier and Mall of Georgia. Beautiful open concept kitchen and dining room. 2-10 Home Warranty is include with this home. The Tesla Charger stays with the home and can work with any EV with an adapter. The surround sound speakers in Living Room stay with Home.
